# Controller Patterns

Controller'lar thin. Route tanımı, decorator'lar, service delegation — başka hiçbir şey.

## Canonical Controller

```typescript
import { Controller, Get, Post, Patch, Delete, Body, Param, Query, HttpCode } from '@nestjs/common';
import { Throttle } from '@nestjs/throttler';
import { CreateUserSchema, UpdateUserSchema, UserListQuerySchema,
         type CreateUserInput, type UpdateUserInput, type UserListQuery } from '@leanmgmt/shared-schemas';
import { Permission } from '@leanmgmt/shared-types';
import { UsersService } from './users.service';
import { RequirePermission } from '@/common/decorators/require-permission.decorator';
import { CurrentUser } from '@/common/decorators/current-user.decorator';
import { Audit } from '@/common/decorators/audit.decorator';
import { ZodValidationPipe } from '@/common/pipes/zod-validation.pipe';
import type { AuthenticatedUser } from '@/common/types';

@Controller('users')
export class UsersController {
  constructor(private readonly usersService: UsersService) {}

  @Get()
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_LIST_VIEW)
  async list(
    @Query(new ZodValidationPipe(UserListQuerySchema)) query: UserListQuery,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.findMany(query, actor);
  }

  @Get(':id')
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_LIST_VIEW)
  async findById(
    @Param('id') id: string,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.findById(id, actor);
  }

  @Post()
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_CREATE)
  @Audit('USER_CREATED', 'USER')
  async create(
    @Body(new ZodValidationPipe(CreateUserSchema)) dto: CreateUserInput,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.create(dto, actor);
  }

  @Patch(':id')
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_UPDATE_ATTRIBUTE)
  @Audit('USER_UPDATED', 'USER')
  async update(
    @Param('id') id: string,
    @Body(new ZodValidationPipe(UpdateUserSchema)) dto: UpdateUserInput,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.update(id, dto, actor);
  }

  @Post(':id/deactivate')
  @RequirePermission(Permission.USER_DEACTIVATE)
  @Audit('USER_DEACTIVATED', 'USER')
  @HttpCode(200)  // default 201 yerine
  async deactivate(
    @Param('id') id: string,
    @Body(new ZodValidationPipe(DeactivateReasonSchema)) dto: DeactivateReasonInput,
    @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser,
  ) {
    return this.usersService.deactivate(id, dto.reason, actor);
  }
}
```

## Required Decorators

Her controller method'unda bir kontrol:

```
Controller method
├── @Get/@Post/@Patch/@Delete (+ route)
├── @RequirePermission(Permission.X) — always required (exception: @Public())
├── @Body/@Query (new ZodValidationPipe(Schema)) — input validation
├── @Audit('ACTION', 'ENTITY_TYPE') — state-changing only
├── @Throttle(...) — sensitive/expensive only
├── @HttpCode(code) — default (200/201) yerine
└── @CurrentUser() actor — almost always need actor identity
```

## Route Conventions

### URL Structure

- `/api/v1/<resource>` — resource root (plural)
- `/api/v1/<resource>/:id` — single resource
- `/api/v1/<resource>/:id/<sub>` — sub-resource
- `/api/v1/<resource>/:id/<action>` — action endpoint

Örnekler:
- `GET /users` — list
- `GET /users/:id` — detail
- `POST /users` — create
- `PATCH /users/:id` — update
- `POST /users/:id/deactivate` — action (değişken durum)
- `GET /users/:id/sessions` — sub-resource
- `POST /users/:id/sessions/:sessionId/revoke` — sub-resource action

### HTTP Methods

- `GET` — read, idempotent, cacheable
- `POST` — create OR non-idempotent action
- `PATCH` — partial update (zorunlu field'lar yok)
- `PUT` — full replacement (nadir kullanılır)
- `DELETE` — soft delete değilse yasak. Genellikle `POST /:id/deactivate` daha açık

### Display ID vs UUID

URL'de UUID kullan. Process için `displayId` daha user-friendly ama internal route'larda UUID:

```typescript
// Internal
@Get('processes/:id')
async findById(@Param('id') id: string) { ... }  // UUID

// User-facing (alternative route)
@Get('processes/by-display-id/:displayId')
async findByDisplayId(@Param('displayId') displayId: string) { ... }
```

Veya tek endpoint + smart parse:

```typescript
@Get('processes/:identifier')
async find(@Param('identifier') identifier: string) {
  if (/^[A-Z]+-\d{6}$/.test(identifier)) {
    return this.service.findByDisplayId(identifier);
  }
  return this.service.findById(identifier);
}
```

## Pagination (Cursor-Based)

Liste endpoint'leri cursor-based pagination:

```typescript
@Get()
@RequirePermission(Permission.USER_LIST_VIEW)
async list(@Query(new ZodValidationPipe(ListQuerySchema)) query: ListQuery) {
  return this.service.findMany(query);
}
```

Query schema:

```typescript
export const ListQuerySchema = z.object({
  limit: z.coerce.number().min(1).max(100).default(20),
  cursor: z.string().optional(),
  companyId: z.string().uuid().optional(),
  isActive: z.coerce.boolean().optional(),
  search: z.string().max(100).optional(),
  sortBy: z.enum(['createdAt', 'lastName', 'sicil']).default('createdAt'),
  sortOrder: z.enum(['asc', 'desc']).default('desc'),
});
```

Response:

```typescript
{
  success: true,
  data: {
    items: [...],
    pagination: {
      nextCursor: "eyJpZCI6Ii4uLiIsInZhbCI6Ii4uLiJ9",
      hasMore: true,
      limit: 20
    }
  }
}
```

Offset-based pagination MVP'de kullanılmaz — büyük offset'te yavaş, unstable when data changes.

## Response Envelope (Automatic)

`ResponseEnvelopeInterceptor` otomatik sarar. Controller sadece `data` kısmını return eder:

```typescript
// Controller return:
return this.service.create(dto, actor);  // UserResponse

// Client receives:
{
  success: true,
  data: { id: "...", sicil: "...", ... }  // UserResponse
}
```

## Error Mapping (Automatic)

`GlobalExceptionFilter` typed exception'ları error envelope'a map eder. Controller `throw` yeter:

```typescript
// Service throws UserSicilDuplicateException
// Filter catches, maps to:
{
  success: false,
  error: {
    code: 'USER_SICIL_DUPLICATE',
    message: 'Bu sicil zaten kayıtlı',
    details: { sicil: '12345678' }
  }
}
// HTTP 409
```

Controller'da manual try/catch YOK (filter handles).

## Validation Errors

Zod validation fail → `ValidationFailedException`:

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_FAILED",
    "message": "Doğrulama hatası",
    "details": {
      "fields": {
        "sicil": "8 haneli numerik olmalı",
        "email": "Geçerli bir e-posta adresi olmalı"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Frontend field-specific error mapping bunu kullanır.

## Rate Limit Application

Default global (600/dk/user). Sensitive endpoint override:

```typescript
// Login — composite limit (IP + email)
@Post('/auth/login')
@Public()
@Throttle({ 
  ip: { limit: 10, ttl: 60_000 },
  email: { limit: 5, ttl: 15 * 60 * 1000 },
})
async login(...) { ... }

// Password reset
@Post('/auth/password-reset-request')
@Public()
@Throttle({ 
  ip: { limit: 5, ttl: 60 * 60 * 1000 },
  email: { limit: 3, ttl: 60 * 60 * 1000 },
})
async requestReset(...) { ... }

// Document upload initiate
@Post('/documents/upload-initiate')
@RequirePermission(Permission.DOCUMENT_UPLOAD)
@Throttle({ default: { limit: 20, ttl: 60_000 } })
async uploadInitiate(...) { ... }
```

## HTTP Status Code Mapping

`AppException.httpStatus` field response status'u belirler:

- 200 — OK (GET, action'lar)
- 201 — Created (POST yeni resource — default)
- 204 — No Content (DELETE, logout)
- 400 — Bad Request (validation)
- 401 — Unauthorized (auth error)
- 403 — Forbidden (permission error)
- 404 — Not Found
- 409 — Conflict (duplicate, state machine violation)
- 410 — Gone (revoked consent version, invalid token)
- 422 — Unprocessable Entity (business rule violation, örn. manager cycle)
- 425 — Too Early (document scan pending)
- 429 — Too Many Requests (rate limit)
- 500 — Internal Server Error (unexpected — Sentry captures)
- 503 — Service Unavailable (maintenance mode)

Bare 500 asla — her error tip typed exception ile mapped.

## Sub-Resource Controllers

Deep nested resource için ayrı controller dosyası:

```typescript
// apps/api/src/users/users-roles.controller.ts
@Controller('users/:userId/roles')
export class UsersRolesController {
  constructor(private readonly service: UserRolesService) {}

  @Get()
  async list(@Param('userId') userId: string, ...) { ... }

  @Post(':roleId')
  @RequirePermission(Permission.ROLE_ASSIGN)
  async assign(@Param('userId') userId: string, @Param('roleId') roleId: string, ...) { ... }

  @Delete(':roleId')
  @RequirePermission(Permission.ROLE_ASSIGN)
  async unassign(...) { ... }
}
```

Her nested resource kendi controller'ı. Tek büyük controller'a zorlamayın.

## Banned Patterns

- `@RequirePermission` atlama (security breach)
- `@Body(...)` olmadan DTO alma (validation bypass)
- Controller'da Prisma kullanmak (service layer bypass)
- `try/catch` inline yazmak — filter'a bırak
- String HTTP status code (`"200"` yerine `HttpStatus.OK` enum)
- Inline Zod schema (shared-schemas'tan import)
- Response manipulation (interceptor'ın işi)
- `console.log` (Pino logger inject et)

